      "parameters": {
        "content": "\n\n\n## Get Ticket Details\nPulls the information included in the the ticket corresponding to the ID. Uses the TDX API.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n* For the URL reference the TDX API Documentation at https://dir.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview or https://dir-test.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview (if testing)\n* add {{$json.TicketID}}\nas a path to the end of the endpoint",
