    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## This Template Demonstrates\nA workflow designed to read and respond to tickets in TDX\n- Scheduled hourly trigger\n- Gathers all tickets in the specific TDX ticket report\n- Gets the information from each ticket\n- Checks if the ticket has already been processed \n- Send the ticket to a helper Maizey to get the information to answer the ticket\n- Uses another Maizey to properly structure the response to the ticket\n- Posts the response to TDX\n- Saves the Ticket ID to a table to prevent reprocessing\n",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 592,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        112,
        896
      ],
      "id": "74266b5d-f631-4c5d-8baa-8b0e3ab8d606",
      "name": "Sticky Note5"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Required Credentials and Scope\n- Umich API Directory\n      - TeamDynamix API credentials used to retrieve ticket information and post responses.\n- Maizey Help\n      - Credentials for a Maizey chatbot project used to retrieve relevant information                          and support ticket response generation.\n- Maizey Ticket Responder\n      - Credentials for a Maizey chatbot project that generates responses to user ticket inquiries.\n",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 608
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        704,
        896
      ],
      "id": "61085dfb-1a91-4429-b741-7d2506eaf378",
      "name": "Sticky Note6"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Ideas and Tips\n- Update the ticket source: set the ticket source for your team's specific report. See details on how to set the credentials\n- Review responses before deploying them to TDX\n- Test the workflow before enabling automated ticket responses in production.\n- Verify duplicate detection: Ensure the processed ticket tracking table is functioning correctly to prevent multiple responses from being posted to the same ticket.\n- Monitor API usage: The workflow uses multiple API calls per ticket. Large ticket volumes may increase processing time and API consumption.",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 608,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1312,
        896
      ],
      "id": "15466989-21d7-41ae-a7bf-298a385ab7bb",
      "name": "Sticky Note20"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Get the Ticket Report From TDX\nPulls up the ticket report using the TDX API.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n* For the URL reference the TDX API Documentation at https://dir.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview\nor https://dir-test.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview (if testing)",
        "height": 672,
        "width": 192,
