    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Maizey Help\nSends the ticket content to the Maizey knowledge base to retrieve relevant context and supporting information. Uses Maizey API.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n* To get the URL for your Maizey reference  https://umgpt.umich.edu/api/schema-public/swagger-ui/",
