    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Refresh Ticket Details\nRetrieves the latest version of the ticket from TDX before posting a response using the TDX API.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n* For the URL reference the TDX API Documentation at https://dir.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview\nor https://dir-test.api.it.umich.edu/docs/tdxticket/1/overview (if testing)\n* Add {{$('Get Ticket Details').item.json.ID}} as the path as the end of the endpoint",
